title: Yeah, No I know The Podcast | PREVIEW
itunes:author: Yeah No I Know, Jenna, Brooklin & Kristen Leanne
description: We are launching episode 1 of Yeah No I Know podcast this coming Tuesday October 10.5! We're new to the podcast world, but we hope we can learn and grow with you. Yeah No I Know is about everything under the sun when it comes to being a woman, a business owner and more. Embarrassing stories are not off the table, actually...nothing is!
